    <!-- DESCRIPTIONS -->
    <string name="desc_mode_reset">
        "Switching modes here will reset all of your timers."
        "You will be prompted again for voting. Simply click the VOTE button"
        "to set another timer."
    </string>
    <string name="desc_normal_mode">
        "Enable a standard 13 hour timer to remind you to vote at each interval."
        "The timer will be reset each time you press the VOTE button."
    </string>
    <string name="desc_opportunistic_mode">
        "Enable a more advanced mode to prompt a vote every time a specific IP address"
        "has not voted after 13 hours. Each time your IP address changes (switching"
        "between WiFi and mobile data), the app will determine if that new IP address"
        "has voted inside 13 hours. If not, a vote prompt will occur. Warning this is a"
        "much more frequent vote reminder than Normal Mode."
    </string>
    <string name="desc_mode">
        "If enabled, ThreshVote will attempt to remind you to vote at every"
        "opportunity. This means that as you move about, getting new IP addresses,"
        "ThreshVote will determine if those new IPs are eligible to vote."
        "If disabled, a standard 13 hour voting window will be put into effect."
    </string>
